title: Guaranteed Admissions Transfer | The University of Illinois at Chicago
text: Required questions are identified with an asterisk (*).

To find out if you qualify for the GAT program please contact your community college advisor or transfer director.  Do you need help finding your transfer director? Not a problem, use the GAT representative directory below by selecting your community college.

If you are in need of further assistance, don’t worry, you can contact UIC GAT staff at by filling out the form on this page or calling 312-355-0564 between 9am - 5pm (CST/CDT).  While you wait for a response be sure to check out the frequently asked questions page for answers to commonly asked question about UIC GAT.
